OL,3,CDriving test rules to change in bid to
OL,4,Ccut backlog and stop bots booking slots
OL,6,FOnly learner drivers will be able to
OL,7,Fbook driving tests in a bid to reduce
OL,8,Flong waiting lists and tackle unfair
OL,9,Fbooking practices.
OL,11,FUnder new government plans,
OL,12,Finstructors will no longer able to
OL,13,Fbook tests on behalf of their students
OL,14,Fand learners will only be able to make
OL,15,Fup to two changes to the driving test
OL,16,Fbooking before it must be cancelled
OL,17,Fand rebooked.
OL,19,FThey will also only be able to move
OL,20,Fthe location of the test to a centre
OL,21,Fnear the original booking.
