OL,3,CDriving test rules to change in bid to
OL,4,Ccut backlog and stop bots booking slots
OL,6,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander
OL,7,Fsaid limiting third parties from
OL,8,Fbooking slots would stop people being
OL,9,F"exploited" by online bots and
OL,10,Fbusinesses which resell test slots at
OL,11,Finflated prices.
OL,13,FAlexander said: "We inherited an
OL,14,Fenormous backlog of learners ready to
OL,15,Fditch their L plates, who have been
OL,16,Fsadly forced to endure record waiting
OL,17,Ftimes for their tests.
OL,19,F"Every learner should have an equal
OL,20,Fand fair opportunity to take a test.
