OL,3,CDriving test rules to change in bid to
OL,4,Ccut backlog and stop bots booking slots
OL,6,F"We're taking decisive action and
OL,7,Fthese new measures will deliver
OL,8,Fthousands of extra tests over the next
OL,9,Fyear, helping learners get on the road
OL,10,Fsooner."
OL,12,FThe average waiting time for a driving
OL,13,Ftest was 21.8 weeks at the end of June.
OL,15,FDriver and Vehicle Standards Agency
OL,16,F(DVSA) figures show the number of
OL,17,Flearner drivers in Britain with a
OL,18,Ffuture test booking as of the end of
OL,19,FOctober was 642,000.
