OL,3,CDriving test rules to change in bid to
OL,4,Ccut backlog and stop bots booking slots
OL,6,FThe total is an indication of the
OL,7,Fbacklog of driving tests, which the
OL,8,FDVSA has attributed to an increase in
OL,9,Fdemand and some people booking tests
OL,10,Fmuch earlier than before.
OL,12,FSome 182,000 tests were conducted in
OL,13,FOctober this year, an increase of 9%
OL,14,Ffrom 168,000 in October 2024.
OL,16,FAlexander told the Commons' Transport
OL,17,FSelect Committee that the Department
OL,18,Ffor Transport's (DfT) target of
OL,19,Freducing the average waiting time for
OL,20,Fbooking a test to seven weeks by
OL,21,Fsummer 2026 will not be met.
