OL,3,CDriving test rules to change in bid to
OL,4,Ccut backlog and stop bots booking slots
OL,6,FAlexander had initially set a target
OL,7,Fof clearing the backlog by the end of
OL,8,Fthis year.
OL,10,FIn addition to the changes around
OL,11,Fbooking tests, 36 military driving
OL,12,Fexaminers from the Ministry of Defence
OL,13,F(MoD) will be brought into the DVSA to
OL,14,Ftry reduce the backlog.
